// Illegal, the default capture has to be the first element in the capture group.
[armor, &](){};Defining new variables in the lambda-captureSometimes we want to capture a variable with a slight modification or declare a new variable that is only visible in the scope of the lambda. We can do so by defining a variable in the lambda-capture without specifying its type.#include <array>
